article.description: — Hunter Maldonado had 21 points as Wyoming topped Cal State Fullerton 79-66 on Monday night.
article.headline: Maldonado leads Wyoming past CSU Fullerton 79-66
article.linkText: Maldonado leads Wyoming past CSU Fullerton 79-66
article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. -- — Hunter Maldonado had 21 points as Wyoming topped Cal State Fullerton 79-66 on Monday night. Graham Ike had 17 points and nine rebounds for the unbeaten Cowboys (6-0). Xavier DuSell added 16 points, while Drake Jeffries scored 14. E.J. Anosike had 19 points for the Titans (3-4).
